    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts reliably, making it an excellent choice for a daily driver or a long-distance cruiser. While the exterior is mostly clean, there are some minor cosmetic imperfections like small paint chips and light scratches typical of a vehicle of this age. The interior is in great shape with all electronics functioning as intended and only minimal wear on the seating surfaces. It is a dependable car that is ready for the road with no immediate repairs necessary.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
